                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/>D<hi rend="tall">i</hi>s Manibus.
                    <lb n="2"/>
               <persName>
                  <name type="praenomen" key="Decimus">
                     <expan>
                        <abbr>D</abbr><ex>ecimus</ex>
                     </expan>
                  </name> 
                  <name type="gentilicium" key="Publicius">Publicius</name>
                    <lb n="3"/>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Aper">Aper</name>
               </persName> armorum custos
                    <lb n="4"/>
               <num xml:lang="lat" value="3">III</num> Soli sibi et <persName>
                  <name>Publiciae</name>
                    <lb n="5"/>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Tyche">Tyche</name>
               </persName> libertae optimae.</ab>
            </div>
        
        
                <div type="translation">
                   <p>To the Divine Spirits. Decimus Publicius Aper, <hi rend="italic">custos armorum</hi>, from the
                      trireme <hi rend="italic">Sol</hi> (made this) for himself and for Publicia Tyche, the best freedwoman.</p>
                </div>
            
        
        
